[{"image":"/images/story12_c_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story12_c_m.mp3",
"text":"不開心時，我可以怎樣做"},
{"image":"/images/story12_p1_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story12_p1_m.mp3",
"text":"小朋友有時會開心"},
{"image":"/images/story12_p2_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story12_p2_m.mp3",
"text":"有時會不開心"},
{"image":"/images/story12_p3_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story12_p3_m.mp3",
"text":"遇到不如意的事情，人人會不開心，我也會不開心，這是一件平常事"},
{"image":"/images/story12_p4_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story12_p4_m.mp3",
"text":"當我不開心，能夠用適當的方法來表達，這是十分重要的"},
{"image":"/images/story12_p5_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story12_p5_m.mp3",
"text":"我可以嘗試用這些方法。一、告訴給大人知道，大人會嘗試明白和幫助小朋友"},
{"image":"/images/story12_p6_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story12_p6_m.mp3",
"text":"二、深呼吸，然後數十下來放鬆"},
{"image":"/images/story12_p7_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story12_p7_m.mp3",
"text":"三、附在桌子上休息一會"},
{"image":"/images/story12_p8_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story12_p8_m.mp3",
"text":"四、要求玩一會兒玩具，忘記不開心的事"},
{"image":"/images/story12_p9_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story12_p9_m.mp3",
"text":"能用這些方法來表達情緒，大人會讚我做的好"}]
